n
T(n)
n<4
T(n-1) + T(n-2) + T(n-3)
n \geq 4
T(1)=1, T(2)=2, T(3)=3
T(4)=T(3)+T(2)+T(1) = 1+1+1+1 = 3
T(5) = T(4)+T(3)+T(2) = 3+1+1 = 5
m\lt n
T(m)\lt 2^m
n=3
T(n)=T(n-1)+T(n-2)+T(n-3)
T(n-1)\lt 2^{n-1},\qquad T(n-2)\lt 2^{n-2},\qquad\text{and}\qquad T(n-3)\lt 2^{n-3}.
2^{n-1}+2^{n-2}+2^{n-3}\lt 2^n
2^{n-1}+2^{n-2}+2^{n-3}=\frac{1}{2}\cdot 2^n+\frac{1}{4}\cdot 2^n+\frac{1}{8}\cdot 2^n=\frac{7}{8}\cdot 2^n\lt 2^n
T(n)\lt 2^{n-1}+2^{n-2}+2^{n-3}.
